snippet.textDisplay: I colored my hair once (a pretty simple thing really, the lower half blue), and while I def had issues with the colored water and the pure paranoia whenever I had to rest my head against something that wasn't blue I also only had to deal with that issue for like two weeks, the color didn't begin to really fade until half a year in because I poured the same blue color into my conditioner. I usually left the colored conditioner in my hair for a couple of minutes before washing it out, just a tip!

The only thing I didn’t regret was getting to color purple that fades into a nice lavender over time.
